{"id":17007,"date":"2024-09-09T11:17:29","date_gmt":"2024-09-09T09:17:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/?p=17007"},"modified":"2024-09-09T11:20:12","modified_gmt":"2024-09-09T09:20:12","slug":"the-chairperson-of-the-national-council-hon-lukas-muha-had-the-honor-of-receiving-a-courtesy-call-from-the-student-representative-council-src-of-the-durban-university-of-technology-dut","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/the-chairperson-of-the-national-council-hon-lukas-muha-had-the-honor-of-receiving-a-courtesy-call-from-the-student-representative-council-src-of-the-durban-university-of-technology-dut\/","title":{"rendered":"The Chairperson of the National Council, Hon. Lukas Muha, had the honor of receiving a courtesy call from the Student Representative Council (SRC) of the Durban University of Technology (DUT)."},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-17008\" src=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/NC-story-300x113.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"113\" \/><\/p>\n<div class=\"xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">The Chairperson of the National Council, Hon. Lukas Muha, had the honor of receiving a courtesy call from the Student Representative Council (SRC) of the Durban University of Technology (DUT).<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">During the meeting, Hon. Muha provided a detailed overview of the mandate of the Parliament of Namibia and shared significant insights into the enduring relationship between Namibia and South Africa. He also encouraged the students to actively engage in leadership and governance roles within Africa.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">The delegation from DUT was accompanied by Dr. Marius Kudumo, Director of Corporate Engagement and International Relations at the University of Namibia (UNAM), and Twapewa-Ashihe Mungoba, President of UNAM\u2019s SRC. The DUT SRC is visiting Namibia as part of an exchange program with UNAM.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">Hon. Muha was joined in this meeting by Adv. Tousy Namiseb, Secretary to the National Council.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The Chairperson of the National Council, Hon. Lukas Muha, had the honor of receiving a courtesy call from the Student Representative Council (SRC) of the Durban University of Technology (DUT). During the meeting, Hon. Muha provided a detailed overview of the mandate of the Parliament of Namibia and shared significant insights into the enduring relationship&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":16,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[159,39],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-17007","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-home-page-slider","category-news","category-159","category-39","description-off"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17007","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/16"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=17007"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17007\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":17011,"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17007\/revisions\/17011"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=17007"}